### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@workspaceId = YOUR_WORKSPACE_ID
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN

### ─── List AI Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### Get all logs (latest 50)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/ai-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── List with filters ────────────────────────────────────────
### Filter by generator (topic | content | campaign)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/ai-logs?generator=content&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Filter by status (success | error)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/ai-logs?status=error&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/ai-logs?limit=10&offset=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Get Log Detail ───────────────────────────────────────────
### Full detail including prompts and response
@logId = YOUR_LOG_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/ai-logs/{{logId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ─── Stats Summary ────────────────────────────────────────────
### Aggregate stats (total, by generator, by provider, error count)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/workspaces/{{workspaceId}}/ai-logs/stats/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
